<book id="GAL"><id id="GAL"> Paul’s Letter to the Galatians
</id><h>((Galatians))
</h><toc level="1">\begin{signline}THE EPISTLE OF PAUL THE APOSTLE TO THE GALATIANS\end{signline}
</toc><toc level="2">((Galatians))
</toc><toc level="3">((Gal))
</toc><p sfm="mt">\begin{signline}THE EPISTLE OF PAUL THE APOSTLE TO THE GALATIANS\end{signline}
